        <h2>> <a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/eZ-Publish-International-showcased-on-Telekom-stage-at-CeBIT-2013" title="eZ Publish International showcased on Telekom stage at CeBIT 2013">eZ Publish International showcased on Telekom stage at CeBIT 2013</a></h2>
     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>eZ Systems’ Monika Binder, Global Business Developer for Telecommunications, explained to the audience how eZ’ Systems’ SaaS product was one of the early partner entries in Deutsche Telekom’s network of cloud service applications that are designed to provide small to medium size enterprises (SMEs) with best fit solutions for tomorrow’s business needs.</p><p>eZ Publish International is a simple pay-as-you-go, responsive design enabled website builder that can publish multiple language pages on the same site and requires no special configuration for publishing to PC, tablet and smartphone. Learning to use the application is very quick; an average user can become fluent in creating, publishing and managing content in just a few hours and adding new content takes just minutes.</p><p>Ms. Binder noted that the partnership with Deutsche Telekom is a positive testimony to the joint efforts of eZ Systems and its wider ecosystem which over 14 years have collectively built a solid software product with a strong service ethos. eZ Systems’ position in the web content management sector and the high flexibility of its core product offering to scale from a highly configurable enterprise platform down to a lite site builder has enabled this team up with the German national carrier to bring to the SME sector a highly reliable website production tool.</p><p>Other application services on the Telekom Business Marketplace include MS Office 365, Box, Symantec and iMeet. The applications selected for inclusion in the marketplace are best in class and are global in origin.</p><div class="separator"><span></span></div><p>Visit <a href="https://portal.telekomcloud.com/" target="_blank">businessmarketplace.de</a> for more information.</p>
    </div>

