        <h2>> <a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/eZ-Systems-GmbH-supports-the-Buergerstiftung-Rheinviertel" title="eZ Systems GmbH supports the “Bürgerstiftung Rheinviertel”">eZ Systems GmbH supports the “Bürgerstiftung Rheinviertel”</a></h2>
     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>Founded in 2005, the community foundation is a unique initiative by citizens for the social, non-profit and charitable functions in the district of Bonn, Bad Godesberg. It shows how much can be achieved, despite empty public coffers, by citizens who become active and shape their future. What all parties have in common is &quot;The Gift To Give&quot; as many citizens bring in their individual talents to support a greater cause.</p><p>The foundation already achieved the sponsorship of three kindergartens as well as the promotion of new educational priorities in a further six kindergartens. All kindergartens offer care for the under threes. Additionally there are full-day courses to improve the compatibility of family and career for working parents. One of the kindergartens is being remodeled into an inclusion-kindergarten for children with and without disabilities.</p><p>The foundation employs two youth consultants that act as contact persons for children and teenagers. Both are furthermore supporting the running of a youth club and center.</p><p>The initiative &quot;In the Middle of Life&quot;, is a valuable contact point for people aged 50 plus.</p><p>The foundation has also helped the establishment of four monasteries that maintain a nationwide pilot project for two &quot;Integrated hospices&quot; that are located in homes for the elderly. A specially trained palliative nurse takes care of a mobile hospice service in the district.</p><p>The many volunteers of the foundation get support from a volunteer-coordinator who also gives impetus to social commitment.</p><div class="separator"><span></span></div><p>As an international company eZ Systems likes to encourage people to take their lives in their hand and to create a better future by joined forces. eZ Systems is excited about the unique initiative of the “Bürgerstiftung Rheinviertel” that supports self-help in the region.</p>
    </div>

