        <h2>> <a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/The-eZ-Publish-Users-Developers-Meetup-group-presents-a-webcast-recording" title="The eZ Publish Users ">The eZ Publish Users </a></h2>
     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>Visit this Youtube video at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6P4xXaQbFOA&feature=youtu.be" target="_self">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6P4xXaQbFOA&feature=youtu.be</a>&nbsp;to watch.</p><p>Gain a better understanding of the features and benefit of eZ Flow, multi-upload, eZ Exceed and several other efficiency driving solutions that eZ Publish offers.</p><p>Get a peek on the workflow of&nbsp;<a href="http://ez.no/Customers/By-Industry/The-Christian-Science-Monitor" target="_self">Christian Science Monitor</a>&nbsp;to see how the&nbsp;<a href="http://ez.no/Products/eZ-Market/Explore-the-eZ-Market/eZ-Collaboration-Workflow" target="_self">eZ Collaboration Workflow</a>&nbsp;extension provides a complex policy and editorial control workflow dashboard solution for this highly respected&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Christian_Science_Monitor#Notable_reporting" target="_self">Pulitzer prize</a>&nbsp;winning USA based news organisation.</p><p>Roland Benedetti, VP of Product&nbsp;Services&nbsp;at eZ Systems gave&nbsp;a presentation on A/B or multivariate testing in eZ Publish. &nbsp;Multivariate testing is the process whereby eZ Publish can be configured to serve multiple variations of a page to your site's visitors,&nbsp;the performance of each of the variations&nbsp;can then be statistically measured with eZ's highly visual and infographic based web analytic tools&nbsp;<a href="http://ez.no/Products/eZ-Market/Explore-the-eZ-Market/eZ-odoscope" target="_self">eZ odoscope: Smart Site Analytics</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="http://ez.no/Products/eZ-Market/Explore-the-eZ-Market/eZ-Live-Viewer" target="_self">eZ Live Viewer</a>. Both analytics tools are tightly integrated right into the heart of the <a href="http://ez.no/Products/eZ-Publish-5-Platform" target="_self">eZ Publish 5 Platform</a>.</p><p>With measurement comes management of websites for both longer term strategic design and short term story management made "on-the-fly" - a unique proposition for a content management solution.</p><p>The&nbsp;<a href="http://www.meetup.com/eZ-Publish-Users-Developers/" target="_self">eZ Publish Users & Developers</a>&nbsp;Meetup group are mostly based in Canada and the USA, but are growing to embrace all in the eZ Publish global user experience community to share best practices and drive more value for the sites you build and the customers that visit them.</p>
    </div>

