    <div class="attribute-header">
        <h2>> <a href="http://ez.no/About-eZ/Events-News/News/eZ-Publish-International-showcase-on-Deutsche-Telekom-s-WebTV-channel" title="eZ Publish International – showcase on Deutsche Telekom's WebTV channel">eZ Publish International – showcase on Deutsche Telekom's WebTV  ...</a></h2>
     </div>

    <div class="attribute-byline">
	    </div>

    

    <div class="attribute-body float-break">
      <p>In July 2012 eZ Systems announced that we entered a partner collaboration with Deutsche Telekom to offer a SaaS (Software as a Service) website building tool that is targeted towards small and medium-sized businesses: eZ Publish International. The service has responsive design to enable publishing to PC, Tablet and Mobile, and enables simple to create multi-lingual websites for organisations wanting to address a multilingual or international audience.</p><p>The service is available via Deutsche Telekom's Business Marketplace, an app store for SaaS solutions selected for SMEs. Here's the entry for eZ Publish International, the edition created for the German market :&nbsp;<a href="https://apps.telekomcloud.com/apps/338?97948664" target="_self">https://apps.telekomcloud.com/apps/338?97948664</a>&nbsp;</p><p>eZ Systems is delighted to share with you a video presentation on&nbsp;DREISECHSNULL, the web TV channel of &nbsp;Deutsche Telekom for small and medium-sized enterprises. Here is the link to watch it:&nbsp;<a href="http://dreisechsnull.telekom.de/#webtv/ez-publish" target="_self">http://dreisechsnull.telekom.de/#webtv/ez-publish</a></p><p>If you have any comments or questions on the service please <a href="/Forms/HTML-forms/Contact-eZ" target="_self">complete this form</a>.</p>
    </div>

